179
00:12:21,890 --> 00:12:26,320
To create a sword like this in an era of firearms and cannons.

180
00:12:26,320 --> 00:12:29,990
I think a man who boasts about overthrowing the Bakufu

181
00:12:29,990 --> 00:12:31,970
