223
00:15:14,660 --> 00:15:17,630
Your skin is as thick as the monthly Shonen JUMP.

224
00:15:14,660 --> 00:15:21,340
[Note: The monthly JUMP is thicker than the weekly JUMP. He's asking if she has thick skin.]

225
00:15:18,280 --> 00:15:21,340
