236
00:15:53,510 --> 00:15:56,810
My brother is an idiot who only cares about making swords.

237
00:15:56,810 --> 00:16:00,150
He wanted to surpass our father, so he was always pounding iron.

238
00:16:00,470 --> 00:16:05,040
