That was around the same time he begun associating with shady people.

240
00:16:07,980 --> 00:16:14,050
I was vaguely aware that they were bad people, but I didn't stop him.

241
00:16:14,050 --> 00:16:17,320
I told myself that all we needed to do was just forge swords.

242
00:16:17,320 --> 00:16:20,130
That's our job...

243
00:16:21,100 --> 00:16:24,690
I knew it. A sword is for butchering people.

244
00:16:24,690 --> 00:16:28,420
It was just a tool for murder.

245
00:16:28,420 --> 00:16:29,820
I knew...

246
00:16:30,630 --> 00:16:33,680
Yet... What a shame...

247
00:16:35,200 --> 00:16:37,870
My brother worked so hard to make that sword...

248
00:16:37,870 --> 00:16:41,110
And it's being used for such a low purpose.

249
00:16:41,790 --> 00:16:45,580
But things are reaching the point where I can't stop it on my own.

250
00:16:46,620 --> 00:16:48,430
I really don't know what to do.

251
00:16:49,090 --> 00:16:51,390
What should I do?

252
00:16:53,360 --> 00:16:56,090
I don't know what to do anymore than you do.

253
00:16:56,360 --> 00:16:58,600
I'm wounded really badly.

254
00:16:58,910 --> 00:17:01,840
And my friend got taken out, too. So I'm not at my best right now.

255
00:17:02,070 --> 00:17:06,920
Here! I don't want your consolation money. Just go home.

256
00:17:07,640 --> 00:17:10,120
I don't want any more trouble.

257
00:17:15,020 --> 00:17:18,280
Since Gin-san is out of action, it's up to me.

258
00:17:18,800 --> 00:17:21,220
There's no doubt that Kagura-chan is on that ship.

259
00:17:21,400 --> 00:17:23,050
But how can I sneak aboard?

260
00:17:23,850 --> 00:17:29,260
This place is crawling with scary looking ronin. What should I do...?

261
00:17:30,530 --> 00:17:33,100
What the hell is that?!

262
00:17:36,490 --> 00:17:40,710
Ow... That bastard, Nizo. He's really out of control.

263
00:17:42,110 --> 00:17:47,230
I wonder if that sword is even safe to use. I could feel the evil in it.

264
00:17:48,500 --> 00:17:49,980
Let me go!

265
00:17:49,980 --> 00:17:53,520
Don't think you'll get away with this!

266
00:17:53,870 --> 00:17:57,690
Don't come crying to me when you're beaten up by Gin-chan!

267
00:17:59,660 --> 00:18:01,880
Geez. She's already wreaking havoc.

268
00:18:01,880 --> 00:18:04,760
That's why I told you we should get rid of her.

269
00:18:04,760 --> 00:18:08,770
Look at what this brat has done to our men, Takechi-senpai!

270
00:18:08,770 --> 00:18:13,060
We can't kill her yet. She has valuable information.

271
00:18:13,060 --> 00:18:20,940
Besides, a girl her age will be in her prime in a few years.

272
00:18:20,940 --> 00:18:24,030
Your Lolita complex is showing again, Senpai.

273
00:18:24,030 --> 00:18:26,950
I don't have a Lolita complex. I'm a feminist.

274
00:18:27,150 --> 00:18:32,110
Look! Her gunshot wound has already healed in just one night

275
00:18:32,110 --> 00:18:37,190
and her extraordinary strength and snow white skin...

276
00:18:37,190 --> 00:18:39,530
Senpai, please cut it out.

277
00:18:39,530 --> 00:18:45,180
No, don't misjudge me. I'm a feminist with a healthy affection for children.

278
00:18:45,180 --> 00:18:48,100
That's someone who has a Lolita complex!

279
00:18:48,100 --> 00:18:49,940
Never mind.

280
00:18:49,940 --> 00:18:52,560
I don't think you understand, idiot.

281
00:18:53,270 --> 00:18:54,750
You're the idiot.

282
00:18:54,750 --> 00:19:00,480
I'm saying those characteristics are prevalent among the Yato clan.

283
00:19:00,480 --> 00:19:01,520
You should die.

284
00:19:01,520 --> 00:19:04,520
Yato... Is that the mercenary clan, Yato?

285
00:19:04,520 --> 00:19:08,070
Does that mean she's a professional assassin who was hired to kill Shinsuke-sama?

286
00:19:08,070 --> 00:19:10,170
Who the hell is she a spy for?

287
00:19:10,170 --> 00:19:13,280
Well, no matter what we asked, she kept saying "zura, zura."

288
00:19:13,280 --> 00:19:15,920
Senpai, she's mocking you.

289
00:19:15,920 --> 00:19:18,470
I don't care whether you're a feminist or have a Lolita complex.

290
00:19:18,470 --> 00:19:24,070
It's really disgusting. I'll show you how easily I handle this girl.

291
00:19:24,070 --> 00:19:24,740
Hey,

292
00:19:24,740 --> 00:19:25,480
...you...

293
00:19:27,210 --> 00:19:28,640
You!

294
00:19:28,640 --> 00:19:31,890
Do you understand your situation?! I'll kill you!

295
00:19:30,760 --> 00:19:34,620
N-No! This girl will be breathtaking in another two or three years.

296
00:19:34,620 --> 00:19:36,980
Don't stop me, Takechi-hentai!

297
00:19:36,980 --> 00:19:39,320
I'm your Senpai, not Hentai!

298
00:19:39,320 --> 00:19:41,070
Hey, who are you, anyway?

299
00:19:41,070 --> 00:19:42,320
You look really suspicious.

300
00:19:42,320 --> 00:19:44,970
You're the most suspicious person I've ever seen in my life!

301
00:19:44,970 --> 00:19:47,630
You look like the ideal picture of a suspicious person.

302
00:19:47,800 --> 00:19:52,010
Whoa! What is that person doing?! Oops, she's not human.

303
00:19:52,010 --> 00:19:53,370
Be careful! She's going to get killed!

304
00:19:53,370 --> 00:19:54,740
[Excuse me. Would you give me some directions?]

305
00:19:55,470 --> 00:19:57,210
[To the entrance of Hell!!]

306
00:20:01,970 --> 00:20:04,570
Phlegm throughout my body, give me strength!

307
00:20:04,570 --> 00:20:05,800
It's so disgusting. Hey, please stop it!

308
00:20:04,690 --> 00:20:07,150
Loogie!!

309
00:20:07,720 --> 00:20:09,720
Eat this!!

310
00:20:13,420 --> 00:20:14,380
What?!

311
00:20:14,380 --> 00:20:15,080
What?!

312
00:20:15,520 --> 00:20:19,070
What do you mean "what?!" You spit all over my face.

313
00:20:19,070 --> 00:20:22,060
Hey, why are you only cleaning off my phlegm?!

314
00:20:22,060 --> 00:20:23,880
It's said, "If you get phlegm on your right cheek,

315
00:20:23,880 --> 00:20:25,870
you should get it on your left cheek, too!"

316
00:20:31,120 --> 00:20:32,590
What are you doing?!

317
00:20:32,590 --> 00:20:34,580
An intruder! Intruder!

318
00:20:34,580 --> 00:20:35,780
Elizabeth...!

319
00:20:39,480 --> 00:20:40,820
[Hurry, go now!]

320
00:20:43,790 --> 00:20:45,920
Elizabeth Senpai!

321
00:20:47,390 --> 00:20:49,120
I'm relieved.

322
00:20:50,000 --> 00:20:53,810
I was afraid you'd try to go out despite your injuries.

323
00:20:56,090 --> 00:20:59,590
You'd die if you went out in your condition.

324
00:20:59,590 --> 00:21:01,140
You're right.

325
00:21:01,140 --> 00:21:04,450
I feel sorry for that girl, but it can't be helped.

326
00:21:07,360 --> 00:21:08,780
...You're right.

327
00:21:09,670 --> 00:21:10,930
Gin-san.

328
00:21:12,290 --> 00:21:14,950
Please don't overdo it.

329
00:21:15,460 --> 00:21:19,360
If you die, Shin-chan and Kagura-chan would be lost without you, Gin-san.

330
00:21:20,200 --> 00:21:21,760
...You're right.

331
00:21:21,760 --> 00:21:25,490
Gin-san, you were pretty wild in your youth,

332
00:21:25,490 --> 00:21:27,880
but you've got to start acting your age now, you know?

333
00:21:27,880 --> 00:21:31,420
That's enough, damn it! I'm not going anywhere,

334
00:21:31,420 --> 00:21:32,770
so just go out and buy me JUMP!

335
00:21:32,770 --> 00:21:35,600
[Note: Akamaru JUMP is the special edition of JUMP.]

336
00:21:32,770 --> 00:21:35,600
The last one you bought was an Akamaru JUMP.

337
00:21:35,600 --> 00:21:37,750
That's the kind of mistake my mom would make!

338
00:21:37,750 --> 00:21:39,910
Yes, yes. I understand.

339
00:21:45,760 --> 00:21:47,030
I'm sorry.

340
00:21:48,880 --> 00:21:50,680
Watch it, moron!

341
00:21:58,500 --> 00:22:01,000
[Wait at the swordsmith's. -Odd Jobs guy]

342
00:22:00,110 --> 00:22:03,920
I hate to behave like an impulsive punk at my age, but....

343
00:22:09,110 --> 00:22:12,110
[This is my favorite umbrella. Please bring it back to me in one piece.]

344
00:22:16,870 --> 00:22:19,730
Tsk... Troublesome woman...

345
00:22:39,170 --> 00:22:40,680
Stupid man...

346
00:24:15,060 --> 00:24:16,900
[THE ANTI-Foreigner FACTION UPRISING]

347
00:24:16,930 --> 00:24:18,740
[A VIOLENT CLASH BETWEEN]

348
00:24:18,800 --> 00:24:20,570
[TWO LARGE FORCES.]

349
00:24:20,600 --> 00:24:21,940
[BENIZAKURA'S...]

350
00:24:22,010 --> 00:24:24,640
[POWER!]

351
00:24:28,240 --> 00:24:30,080
[The next episode... "The Sun Will Rise Again"]

352
00:24:30,080 --> 00:24:35,020
[After the Benizakura takes over part of Nizo, it'll become a monster.]

353
00:24:35,020 --> 00:24:40,020
[Takasugi's beast continues to cry. Hurry up, Gintoki. Before everything is destroyed.]
